sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant FE as Frontend
    participant BE as Backend (Django)
    participant DS as DocumentService
    participant FS as FormulaService
    participant SUM as Summarizer

    U->>FE: Login/Register
    FE->>BE: POST /api/auth/login or /register
    BE-->>FE: Auth token

    U->>FE: Upload documents (PDF/Word/Text)
    FE->>BE: POST /api/documents/ (multipart)
    BE->>DS: Save file, parse content
    DS->>SUM: Generate summary
    SUM-->>DS: Summary text
    DS-->>BE: Document object with summary
    BE-->>FE: Document list with summaries

    U->>FE: View document summaries
    FE->>BE: GET /api/documents/
    BE-->>FE: List of documents with summaries

    U->>FE: Create/Edit formula
    FE->>BE: POST/PUT /api/formulas/
    BE->>FS: Validate and save formula
    FS-->>BE: Formula object
    BE-->>FE: Updated formula list

    U->>FE: Calculate using formula
    FE->>BE: POST /api/formulas/{id}/calculate
    BE->>FS: Evaluate formula with inputs
    FS-->>BE: Calculation result
    BE-->>FE: Result

    U->>FE: Share formula
    FE->>BE: POST /api/formulas/{id}/share
    BE->>FS: Share with user/team
    FS-->>BE: Success
    BE-->>FE: Confirmation
